00:12:34.960 --> 00:12:36.479
hid all the evidence?

00:12:37.799 --> 00:12:39.239
I told you, I didn't kill anyone.

00:12:40.679 --> 00:12:41.760
I didn't kill her.

00:12:41.760 --> 00:12:43.000
I already told you.

00:12:45.359 --> 00:12:46.280
It was Xu Libin.

00:12:46.679 --> 00:12:47.880
Xu Libin did it.

00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:53.679
Xu Libin,

00:12:54.440 --> 00:12:55.239
don't play dumb.

00:12:56.919 --> 00:12:58.760
This is Cao Feng's trekking pole, right?

00:12:59.119 --> 00:13:00.440
The injury on Wang Yizhuo's head

00:13:00.440 --> 00:13:01.479
was caused by this thing,

00:13:01.479 --> 00:13:02.280
right?

00:13:02.559 --> 00:13:03.799
No, no, no, I don't know.

00:13:03.799 --> 00:13:04.919
I don't know anything.

00:13:05.239 --> 00:13:07.280
You were at the scene then, right?

00:13:08.559 --> 00:13:10.719
I said I don't know, officer.

00:13:10.719 --> 00:13:12.200
I don't know any of this.

00:13:12.400 --> 00:13:13.520
I don't know.

00:13:14.119 --> 00:13:14.640
Officer.

00:13:24.280 --> 00:13:25.080
Xu Libin,

00:13:28.919 --> 00:13:30.880
I know you're scared.

00:13:30.880 --> 00:13:32.880
But you also need to know

00:13:33.400 --> 00:13:34.960
covering up a crime

00:13:35.640 --> 00:13:37.320
will also land you in prison.

00:13:40.679 --> 00:13:42.039
And let me tell you this.

00:13:44.719 --> 00:13:46.679
Cao Feng has already confessed everything.

00:13:46.679 --> 00:13:47.719
He put all the blame

00:13:47.719 --> 00:13:49.239
onto you.

00:13:49.239 --> 00:13:51.159
He said you killed her.